     racenum so existing characters keep their tribe. Display names live in
     cfg/messages/ru/pc_race_msg.xml (keyed by the same vnum). place_of_birth lists the race's birth
     cities (cities.xml ids) -- one per region the race spans; the player chooses the region and the
     race fixes the village. feature id = EFeat token. -->
